        },
        {
          "stepDescription": "Add bhindi and salt. Mix it well. Cover and cook on a medium flame for 5 mins. Then saute without covering for another 15-20 mins, till the bhindi becomes crispy. Switch off the stove and sprinkle lemon juice. Serve hot.",
